OL,3,C'It's one of my happy days': Father of
OL,4,Cmissing man on charity motorbike ride
OL,6,FAround 250 motorbikers gathered in
OL,7,Fmemory of a missing man from Wiltshire.
OL,9,FBen Garland, from Southwick in
OL,10,FWiltshire, went missing off the coast
OL,11,Fof northern Ibiza in January 2020.
OL,13,FHis motorbike and other belongings
OL,14,Fwere found a few days later, but Ben
OL,15,Fremains missing.
OL,17,FIn August 2021, Ride to the Tide was
OL,18,Fborn - a group motorbike ride held in
OL,19,FBen's honour, raising money for the
OL,20,FRNLI.
