OL,3,C'It's one of my happy days': Father of
OL,4,Cmissing man on charity motorbike ride
OL,6,FNow on its fourth year, the ride is
OL,7,Fattended by around 250 people.
OL,9,FThis year the ride was held on
OL,10,FSaturday 17 August. Riders meet up at
OL,11,FTrowbridge Rugby Club, and then finish
OL,12,Fin Poole.
OL,14,FMark Garland, Ben's father, said each
OL,15,Fyear the event grows.
OL,17,F"We are hoping this year will be a
OL,18,Fbumper year and a lot bigger than the
OL,19,Fprevious years so hopefully we can
OL,20,Fsmash it this year.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
