OL,3,C'It's one of my happy days': Father of
OL,4,Cmissing man on charity motorbike ride
OL,6,F"Word's out now and we have sort of
OL,7,Fbuilt up a bit of a reputation. I do
OL,8,Fsee a lot of posts on social media
OL,9,Fsaying that it is a well-organised
OL,10,Fride and it's all for a good cause.
OL,12,F"I see somebody quoted it as 'the
OL,13,Fbiggest ride out in the south west', I
OL,14,Fwill hold judgement on that.
OL,16,F"It is getting bigger, and it is also
OL,17,Fknown. You mention the name to people,
OL,18,Fand they are aware of what it is and
OL,19,Fwhat it is about.
