OL,3,C'It's one of my happy days': Father of
OL,4,Cmissing man on charity motorbike ride
OL,6,F"Ben was a local lad and he was well
OL,7,Fknown within the local community and
OL,8,Fthe biker community especially, and a
OL,9,Flot of people had a lot of respect for
OL,10,Fhim.
OL,12,F"He was a good lad and sadly taken way
OL,13,Fbefore his time, which is a great loss
OL,14,Ffor me and all his friends and family."
OL,16,FNot only has Mark had to cope with
OL,17,FBen's disappearance, he lost his
OL,18,Fdaughter to breast cancer.
OL,20,F"The last four and a half years this
OL,21,Fhas all been very tough for me.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@gO]|D@AOU
