OL,3,C'It's one of my happy days': Father of
OL,4,Cmissing man on charity motorbike ride
OL,6,F"Never having Ben's body is the
OL,7,Fhardest thing for any sort of parent
OL,8,Fto deal with, that was hard enough.
OL,9,FBut then two and a half years later, I
OL,10,Flost my daughter Charlotte to breast
OL,11,Fcancer, so its really hit me hard over
OL,12,Fthe four years.
OL,14,F"But I remain positive, I have to. I
OL,15,Fhave to stay strong for the rest of my
OL,16,Ffamily."
OL,18,FMoving forward, Ride to the Tide is
OL,19,Fone of Mark's favourite days.
