OL,3,C'It's one of my happy days': Father of
OL,4,Cmissing man on charity motorbike ride
OL,6,F"It's one of my happy days of the
OL,7,Fyear. I don't have too many nowadays
OL,8,Fbut this is one of them.
OL,10,F"When I see all of them bikes, and I
OL,11,Fsee everyone there all basically for
OL,12,FBen and for the RNLI, it makes me very
OL,13,Fhappy to see that."
